[left][b]Summary:[/b] The server I am making will be a 317 loading 634 items and cache. I am still deciding on how I will make the server's economy stable, but what I know so far is all skill will be working and I wont be adding summoning or newer runescape stats.
[b]Base:[/b] The base I am going to use is Project Insanity [PI]. I was planning on using the source Extrania because it has netty implemented in the server. The server must be stable because I am planning on going big on this project. [/left] [left]
